": false, "likes": 2155}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASG4uzdUw", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 41, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "pocrime", "id": 8465872, "raw_content": "I've been actively monitoring it, and they're seemingly letting things slide, and you know where that leads. It seems like they are quietly hoping it works and people do start activating like terrorist cells. We've seen nonchalant and open calls to persuade people inside the US and Europe to rise up and attack government and military. There are videos that get hundreds of thousands of views and don't get taken down, despite being obvious calls to terrorism. \r\n\r\nTrump needs to get on this ASAP and come down on them hard. ", "author": "preferredfault", "created": 1772650827177, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "CleanUpPhillyTrump24", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Blowing the whistle: Youtube is not stopping videos calling for people to rise up and do terrorism on American soil...", "last_comment_created": 1772653362906, "content": "<p>I've been actively monitoring it, and they're seemingly letting things slide, and you know where that leads. It seems like they are quietly hoping it works and people do start activating like terrorist cells. We've seen nonchalant and open calls to persuade people inside the US and Europe to rise up and attack government and military. There are videos that get hundreds of thousands of views and don't get taken down, despite being obvious calls to terrorism.</p>\n<p>Trump needs to get on this ASAP and come down on them hard.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 41, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "\ud83d\udea8\u00a0\u00a0LOCK THEM UP\u00a0\u00a0\ud83d\udea8", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASG4uyoPx", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 56, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8465581, "raw_content": "", "author": "TheBeerJoo", "created": 1772643986934, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASG4uyoPx.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/KZ9qofpqHJSn.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/5Jj6aqqttvs6tCqV.png", "width": 768, "content-type": "png", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "U9N,PVD4?[kq[LHX02R..RMw#-aeGYb^.7i_", "full_resolution": [1024, 1024]}, "title": "Dear President Trump, listening to the Canadian Prime Minister's Comments, it is more obvious NOW then ever that NATO has outlived its value. Entirely. It must be dissolved and replaced with a new alliance of nations that DO IN FACT SHARE USA's VALUES.. Especially Free Speech.", "last_comment_created": 1772643986934, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 0, "score_up": 56, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASG4uyWyH", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 70, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8465429, "raw_content": "I'm just pasting a message I sent to a friend. But it's what just happened.\nWho can I call and speak to to report this shit to?????\nI just called the VA and the main fiduciary hub that handles payments to disabled vets. The VA rep had a very strong Hong Kong accent, impatient and just wanted to get it done, but did do his job. Then connected me to the main fiduciary center. Indian accent guy. Also impatient but answered all my questions the same. Both were given his full name, DOB, military branch and SSN.\nThe Indian guy then thought he hung up but hadn't! I sat there listening for almost 10 minutes while he ate....snorted, clanged his dishes, chewed, swallowed.....I could hear it all! Imagining what kind of curry he was having.\nThen at the end a sudden ..... \"Oh!\" And he hung up.\nObviously an at home call worker , probably in another country and getting such information and giving me feedback from government data he's looking up on his computer!\nWTF!\nWho can I trust to call to report or complain to???\nThis is crazy. My veteran brother died and I'm reporting in to foreigners!!!! To make sure everything is being done correctly with the fudituary who was giving his widow attitude when she inquired as to what to do next. Maybe the fudituary is also overseas?\n", "author": "USMC6541E5", "created": 1772639556933, "profile_picture": "8W4BNLRnoEkC", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DebbieinDallas", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "I need advice. My disabled veteran brother died last week. I called VA and was answered by \"at home\" call workers eating. Hong Kong and Indian accents.", "last_comment_created": 1772648984476, "content": "<p>I'm just pasting a message I sent to a friend. But it's what just happened.\nWho can I call and speak to to report this shit to?????\nI just called the VA and the main fiduciary hub that handles payments to disabled vets. The VA rep had a very strong Hong Kong accent, impatient and just wanted to get it done, but did do his job. Then connected me to the main fiduciary center. Indian accent guy. Also impatient but answered all my questions the same. Both were given his full name, DOB, military branch and SSN.\nThe Indian guy then thought he hung up but hadn't! I sat there listening for almost 10 minutes while he ate....snorted, clanged his dishes, chewed, swallowed.....I could hear it all! Imagining what kind of curry he was having.\nThen at the end a sudden ..... &quot;Oh!&quot; And he hung up.\nObviously an at home call worker , probably in another country and getting such information and giving me feedback from government data he's looking up on his computer!\nWTF!\nWho can I trust to call to report or complain to???\nThis is crazy. My veteran brother died and I'm reporting in to foreigners!!!! To make sure everything is being done correctly with the fudituary who was giving his widow attitude when she inquired as to what to do next. Maybe the fudituary is also overseas?</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 8, "score_up": 70, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2028989164843094419", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASG4siqSR", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 1026, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_clas